@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_wwazib(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v1
    v1 = (v2 * (wp.sin(v2 + 0.99) - (v1 + 0.91 + v0 + 0.49)))
    tmp = 0.68
    v1 = v1
    v1 = wp.sin((wp.abs(v2 + 0.27) / (v1 + 0.19 - v1 + 0.88)))
    v0 = v1
    v0 = 0.40
    data[tid] = v0
